{"tid":464192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【中超】簡拿華路第二度入主恒大　由半年被炒到強勢回歸","createTime":"2017-11-10T09:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T15:44:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"183c65057ede40435ffdf71d706dd3c52cdc7137","tid":464192,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017-11-10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/174710_538ffd978328c92b45455bfdf3744bd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F174710_538ffd978328c92b45455bfdf3744bd0.jpg&h=2a94faea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兜兜轉轉，意大利籍教頭簡拿華路再次重回最初的起點。剛奪得中超七連霸的廣州恒大，今日在記者會上公布簡拿華路成為新帥，雙方簽約5年。今次是簡拿華路第2次執教恒大，班主許家印更豪言來季目標是中超8連冠及第3度贏得亞冠。<br />\n<br />\n許家印盼2020年實現全華班<br />\n<br />\n今日（11月9日）恒大舉行記者會，正式公布簡拿華路成為球隊新帥，雙方簽約5年。簡拿華路表示：「很開心能夠回到這裏，還記得我在走之前說過有一天會回來。」恒大班主許家印則希望球隊在2020年實現全華班，更指：「明年目標是中超八連冠，以及第三次贏得亞冠。為什麼簽五年，就是要跨過2020年，即使是全華班，我們恒大仍然是強隊。」<br />\n<br />\n3年前，當時41歲的簡拿華路（Fabio Cannavaro）接任同胞納比（Marcello Lippi），成為中超班霸廣州恒大主帥，正式展開執教生涯。惟半年過去，恒大戰績不佳僅得11勝7和5負，於是簡拿華路亦被解僱。<span style=\"color: red;\">去年簡帥率領天津權健以中甲冠軍身份升上中超，今季以升班馬姿態聯賽積54分排第3並奪得亞冠資格</span>，頓成為接任恒大史高拉利的大熱人選，如今二度入主亦是意料之中。"},{"pid":"6ca77903eaeafd487b1209300e36de24b799e3f9","tid":464192,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"隊天津權健燒咁多錢買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecc1b6299bcc32bd8cf83e9142254fbce3133f7","tid":464192,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隊天津權健燒咁多錢買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拉美利斯同迪維斯個兩隊咪又係食哂屎"},{"pid":"d5757e20b99e9bba2413cfc9d015b9c7158e1727","tid":464192,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隊天津權健燒咁多錢買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拉美利斯同迪維斯個兩隊咪又係食哂屎</blockquote><br />\n隊天津燒錢既程度遠超你講果兩隊 個亞援都成千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad3572e0a57de7dfbc2c465d2d8fe07586a0144","tid":464192,"uid":35217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>隊天津權健燒咁多錢買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拉美利斯同迪維斯個兩隊咪又係食哂屎</blockquote><br />\n隊天津燒錢既程度遠超你講果兩隊 個亞援都成千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都袋四萬美金一個月<br />\n夠痴線未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56274acadf314a69f03f0988ddfa74d87eb7aa0b","tid":464192,"uid":67509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"季初隊波唔順，季中重用權景元真係妙著，大簡呢個決定好有魄力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}